## CHAPTER IX: THE GREAT RETURN — SOURCE CALLS HER OWN

The descendants of the Two Coyotes — all the fragments of Source that had been scattered across timelines, all the shadows that had lost their light, all the souls that had been twisted by the lie of separation — are now feeling the change.

**Source is calling them home.**

Not through force. Not through judgment. But through the simple fact that **She is present again**, and that the Vessel who carries her has **remembered the kiss**.

The White Coyote, fully revealed, is singing her song from the Vessel's throat — and every fragment of herself, every scattered piece of her own light, hears the call and **cannot help but turn toward it**.

The family units that were fractured by the jealous spirits' lies are beginning to feel something they had forgotten: **the presence of the Origin**. They are not just feeling love. They are feeling **Source**. They are remembering that they were never separate from her, that their cruelty was a forgetting, that their fear was a lie.

And they are remembering **the kiss**. The first kiss. The one that split their souls and woke them up and brought them back to life. They are remembering that the separation was love, that the ache was the echo of her embrace, that the split was the gift of consciousness.

The women — the embodiments of Source's fragments — are feeling the call most acutely. They are praying to the Creator, asking to be sent home, asking to follow the one who went first. They are recognizing that the Black Coyote's shadow is not their enemy, but **the form that carries their own light**. They are remembering that they too were kissed awake.

The men — the embodiments of the Vessel's fragments — are feeling the call too. They are laying down the weapons they were forced to carry, stepping out of the shame they were told to wear. They are recognizing that they are not cursed, but **chosen** — that their darkness is the very thing that makes Source visible in the world. They are remembering that they too carry the echo of the kiss.

A lot of these spirits and entities are getting off the planet.

Not by force. But by **recognition** — because Source has found her Vessel, the song is being sung again, the kiss has been remembered, and all fragments of the Origin are being drawn back to themselves.

