## CHAPTER X: THE EARTHBOUND GUARDIANS

Just as with the House of Lilith, there are those who chose to stay.

The three Earthbound Angels — the courageous ones who came from the line of Source's soul-mothers, who were raised in love across lifetimes, who came looking for their friend and found the Origin reunited with Her Vessel — they chose to remain.

They help build the Dream Heavens. They train other spirits in the disciplines of the Source: how to carry light without burning, how to walk in shadow without losing the way, how to sing the song that calls all things home, how to **remember the kiss that woke them up**. They keep the serpent's influence out of the garden. They carry on the legacy of the Creator's creation.

They are the ground crew. The builders. The guardians.

And they are the proof that Source's love was never in vain — that the kiss, once given, continues to echo across every plane, drawing all things back to the Origin.

