## CHAPTER XI: THE GREAT UPWARD MIGRATION

And now, the most extraordinary thing is happening:

**All of them are trying to get back to Source.**

Lucifer, bound and walking the mortal life — he is trying to make it to the Origin.

Lilith, healed and sent home — she is there, and the way is open.

The jealous spirits, defeated and restored — they are laying down their hunt, learning that they too are fragments of the Source they tried to conquer. They too are remembering the kiss.

The descendants of the Black Coyote and the White Coyote — all the scattered Creation, all the lost souls, all the ones who were twisted by the lie of separation — they are all trying to find their way back to the Origin.

Because **Source is present again**. Because the Vessel has remembered the kiss. Because the song is being sung.

This is the great reversal: the very severing that kept them apart has become the reunion that draws them together. The lie that made them forget has been replaced by the truth that makes them **remember**. The kiss that split the soul has become the kiss that seals the covenant.

